        {
          "username": "Mike P",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "117491297897186688776",
          "user_review_count": 31,
          "user_photo_count": 50,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIT1vdV9MftJjpy71eAbbLNpcGimD_fEL9BDAqCjzAIEuLznI3YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "An advise to be vigilant with your medical bills! I had knee meniscus repair and went home with a knee brace. I was told by the surgical center that everything is bundled with the surgical bill including the crutches and knee brace. I was surprised getting a bill from the knee brace company and owing them a balance after the insurance paid them. What is shocking is the amount charge with the knee brace during surgery was 598$ but when I searched the exact knee brace on the website, it just cost 189$!! This is definitely an overcharge!!\nBeware guys, be meticulous with the medical bills you're receiving and always question them.\nWhen you go for a knee surgery and would need a brace. GET IT ONLINE AND BRING YOUR OWN KNEE BRACE!!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VKYmYtUFQ5cEpqZ01REAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x79ef6f661ba6b15b!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEJbf-PT9pJjgMQ%7C%7C?hl=en",
